<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="CH1a0930-zh-bdaec342" type="transl"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>Translation of 鬼谷子 into (Chinese)</title><editor role="translator">Yan Chongdong 1998</editor></titleStmt><publicationStmt><ab>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org</ab><availability status="4">The copyright status of this work is unclear</availability></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><bibl><title>閻崇動《鬼谷子詞典》</title>湖北人民，1998</bibl><ab>Translation of <bibl corresp="#CH1a0930"><title xml:lang="och">鬼谷子</title></bibl> into <lang xml:lang="zh">Chinese</lang>.</ab></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><creation resp="#CH">Initially created: <date>2023-01-01T21:34:52.399+09:00</date> by CH</creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div><head>Translated parts</head><p xml:id="CH1a0930-start"><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-01-01T21:36:23.153+09:00">至於考研過去的歷史</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-01-01T21:37:06.108+09:00">降臨於天地間的聖人，</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-01-01T21:38:03.523+09:00">就是世人的先知先覺。</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-01-01T21:39:35.008+09:00">根據陰陽兩個方面的開啟與閉合來命名辨別萬事萬物。</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-01-01T21:40:57.034+09:00">要拿握事物存與亡的要領和道理，</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-01-01T21:41:49.747+09:00">了解萬物起始與衰亡的過程，</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-01-01T21:42:24.934+09:00">通達人們內心的活動規律，</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-01-01T21:43:33.552+09:00">觀察各種現象變化發展的徵兆，</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-01-01T21:44:47.251+09:00">從而堅守和把握它們的要領和關鍵。</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-01-01T21:45:11.377+09:00">所以聖人來到天下，</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-01-01T21:45:25.292+09:00">從古到今，</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-01-01T21:47:10.397+09:00">它們統治和管理的規律是一致的。</seg></p></div></body></text></TEI>